title: The 2015 Heisman Trophy tracker, Week 8: Former Logan High star shoots up the list
text:
A look at how the leading candidates for the 2015 Heisman Trophy performed during an exciting weekend of college football.
Upcoming Games Utah Football Utah football stats & schedule Ore. St. @ Utah Rice-Eccles Stadium, Salt Lake City Oct. 31, 5:00 p.m. 5 Days 3 Hrs 44 Mins 12 Secs More Coverage What you may have missed: A chronological recap of the Utes' first loss through the Twitter lens Week 8 of the college football season brought some wild finishes, a couple of shocking outcomes and an injury that could derail championship dreams for one of the best teams in the country. It also provided plenty of star power as some of the game's biggest and brightest had big performances in carrying their teams to victory.
Here is my ranking of the top contenders for the Heisman Trophy after the eighth weekend.
